# MFOI Database Configuration
# Choose ONE of the following options:

# ==================================================
# OPTION 1: Supabase (Recommended - includes Auth)
# ==================================================
# Get these from: https://supabase.com → Your Project → Settings → API
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-id.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-public-key-here

# ==================================================
# OPTION 2: LocalStorage Only (No cloud sync)
# ==================================================
# Leave all variables above empty to use localStorage only
# Data stays on your browser - 100% free, works offline
# Note: LocalStorage mode doesn't support multi-device sync